OL,3,CScotland's North Sea dilemma: Where
OL,4,Crising bills meet rising tides
OL,6,FUnder Nicola Sturgeon, the party grew
OL,7,Fincreasingly hostile to the oil and
OL,8,Fgas industry. When the UK government
OL,9,Fapproved the Cambo oil field, Sturgeon
OL,10,Furged Boris Johnson to reconsider.
OL,11,FWhen Rosebank was approved in
OL,12,FSeptember 2023, she described it as
OL,13,Fthe "greatest act of environmental
OL,14,Fvandalism" of her lifetime.
OL,16,FHer successor, Humza Yousaf, went
OL,17,Ffurther still, calling supporters of
OL,18,Fnew North Sea oil and gas production
OL,19,F"climate deniers".
OL,26,@uD@EOUvD@JO]{D@AOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776477807
OL,3,CScotland's North Sea dilemma: Where
OL,4,Crising bills meet rising tides
OL,6,FAt a climate conference in New York,
OL,7,Fhe also declared his ambition for
OL,8,FScotland to stop being the "oil and
OL,9,Fgas capital" of Europe and become
OL,10,Finstead its "net zero capital".
OL,12,FThe SNP formally adopted a
OL,13,F'presumption against' policy when it
OL,14,Fcame to new oil and gas development as
OL,15,Fpart of its draft energy strategy.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@LO]rD@MOUrD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776477807
OL,3,CScotland's North Sea dilemma: Where
OL,4,Crising bills meet rising tides
OL,6,FBut the change of heart from the SNP
OL,7,Fnow creates a new problem: the
OL,8,FScottish Greens are furious about it,
OL,9,Fand Swinney may be relying on their
OL,10,Fsupport if he is to become First
OL,11,FMinister again.
OL,13,F"If they want the support of the
OL,14,FGreens, clearly they need to be a
OL,15,Fgovernment to tackling the climate
OL,16,Femergency," says Scottish Greens co-
OL,17,Fleader, Ross Greer.
OL,19,FHe adds: "This isn't Nicola Sturgeon's
OL,20,FSNP anymore."
OL,26,@uD@AOUxD@KO]{D@JOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776477807
OL,3,CScotland's North Sea dilemma: Where
OL,4,Crising bills meet rising tides
OL,6,FThe SNP is not alone in repositioning,
OL,7,Fthough. Across the political spectrum,
OL,8,Fthe case for new North Sea development
OL,9,Fis gaining ground.
OL,11,FThe Scottish Liberal Democrats went
OL,12,Ffrom being ardent opponents to now
OL,13,Fsaying they could see merit in
OL,14,Fdeveloping new fields at Rosebank and
OL,15,FJackdaw because it may be the "least
OL,16,Fbad" environmental option while the UK
OL,17,Fstill needs oil and gas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776477807
OL,3,CScotland's North Sea dilemma: Where
OL,4,Crising bills meet rising tides
OL,6,FThe Scottish Conservatives have
OL,7,Fembraced Donald Trump's "drill baby
OL,8,Fdrill" stance, pointing to the jobs
OL,9,Fnew fields would create.
OL,11,FReform argue the UK's emissions are
OL,12,Ftoo small globally to justify holding
OL,13,Fback while relying on imports.
OL,15,FEven Scottish Labour leader Anas
OL,16,FSarwar has broken from his own party,
OL,17,Furging Energy Secretary Ed Miliband to
OL,18,Fapprove new licences.
OL,26,@oD@YOUpD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776477807
OL,3,CScotland's North Sea dilemma: Where
OL,4,Crising bills meet rising tides
OL,6,FThe decision on North Sea licensing
OL,7,Fremains reserved to Westminster,
OL,8,Fmeaning Holyrood cannot act
OL,9,Funilaterally regardless of who wins in
OL,10,FScotland. But the direction of
OL,11,Fpolitical travel could not be clearer
OL,12,Fin Scotland.
OL,14,FThe two fields at the centre of this
OL,15,Fdebate are Rosebank, west of Shetland,
OL,16,Fand Jackdaw, east of Aberdeen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
