FL,350,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31917
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776477807
OL,3,CScotland's North Sea dilemma: Where
OL,4,Crising bills meet rising tides
OL,6,FThe science linking fossil fuels to a
OL,7,Fwarming planet has not changed. But
OL,8,Fthe political sands have shifted, and
OL,9,Fafter this election, decisions will be
OL,10,Ftaken that could shape Scotland's
OL,11,Fcoastline, and its economy, for a
OL,12,Fgeneration.
OL,14,FFrom Westminster to Washington DC -
OL,15,Four political experts are across all
OL,16,Fthe latest key talking points. Listen
OL,17,Fto the latest episode below...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G17/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
